description: Coated in crunchy coconut and quinoa, this crumbed chicken is delicious served with a side of tangy tomato chutney.
name: Quinoa & CoconutCrumbed Chicken Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 500 g Macro Organic chicken breast fillets

recipeInstructions.text: Spray chicken with oil. Bake for 20 minutes, turning and spraying chicken with oil halfway through cooking, or until chicken is light golden and cooked through. Sprinkled chicken with parsley and serve with chutney.
